HEADWORD: Drawrod
<hw>Draw"rod`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Railroad)</fld>
<def>A rod which unites the drawgear at opposite ends of the car, and
bears the pull required to draw the train.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Drawshave</ent>⟦br⟧
